(1739, 'Rahul', 'growth@skymooninfotech.com', '84289234484', '-', '-', 'Opportunity Knocks: Transform Your Startup\'s Future', 'Hey Startup Leader! Get a FREE personalized report from Skymoon Infotech! Ready to Propel Your Business Forward? Discover how our expert strategies in website design, SEO, and performance marketing can elevate your business to new heights. Don\'t miss out РђЊ claim your report now and let\'s unlock your full potential! \r\n \r\nP.S. If you think i have wasted your time on call i will pay you $100 \r\n \r\nBest regards, \r\nRahul \r\nMarketing Head \r\nSkymoon Infotech \r\n \r\ngrowth@skymooninfotech.com \r\nhttp://www.skymooninfotech.com/', '2024-03-27 08:23:01', '2024-03-27 08:23:01'),
