(2487, 'Emily Cooper', 'emily.cooper@gummicube.com', '0000000000', 'mobile-app-development', 'Gummicube', 'Blog Collaboration', 'IРђЎm Emily Cooper, Content Coordinator at GummicubeРђЊ an industry-leading, full-service App Store Optimization company.\r\n\r\nIРђЎm reaching out because weРђЎd love to contribute to your blog if youРђЎre open to new guest authors. Through our posts, we have provided a ton of value to large companies and startups alike who are trying to increase their app store reach and conversions. It would be a great opportunity to provide your readers with information about how they can apply different App Store Optimization strategies to their projects as well.\r\n\r\nIРђЎd be glad to discuss in the coming days over a call how we can collaborate for your blog. Thank you in advance and I look forward to hearing back from you!\r\n\r\nBest,\r\nEmily Cooper', '2024-11-12 16:37:17', '2024-11-12 16:37:17'),
