(2736, 'Katja McGrowdie', 'mcgrowdie.katja@gmail.com', 'Roxsvofsjmm', 'connected-devices', 'Katja McGrowdie', 'Quick question?', 'Hey there, I came across your website and was impressedРђћgreat work!\r\n\r\nI know your time is valuable, so IРђЎll be brief.\r\n\r\nAI is essential for business growth, and many owners struggle to know where to startРђћthatРђЎs why IРђЎm here to help.\r\n\r\nWeРђЎve created two guides called AI For Entrepreneurs and Smarter with AI, normally priced at $29 each, and we\'re offering it to you for free. Inside, youРђЎll discover:\r\n\r\n    + How to quickly increase your business/website revenue.\r\n    + A simple framework for incorporating AI into your business.\r\n    + Proven strategies to boost productivity and save time.\r\n    + Expert tips to get results, whether you\'re just starting or well-established.\r\n\r\nRemember, this is absolutely free and will cost you nothing! \r\n\r\nWould you like a free copy?\r\n\r\nGet yor guide here: http://aibusinessmastery.pro\r\n\r\nIРђЎm confident itРђЎll be a game-changer for you, and IРђЎd love to hear how it works for your business!\r\n\r\nBest regards', '2025-03-03 21:43:33', '2025-03-03 21:43:33'),
