(2965, 'Rashid Minhas Sheikh', 'rashidminhassheikh47@gmail.com', '03154727626', '-', '-', 'Application for Remote Flutter Developer Position', 'Dear AppsNation Team,\r\n\r\nI am writing to express my interest in a remote Flutter Developer position at your organization. With over 5 years of professional experience in mobile and cross-platform application development, I bring a broad and deep skill set focused on delivering high-performance, scalable, and user-friendly applications using Flutter and Firebase.\r\n\r\nThroughout my career, I have successfully led and contributed to a wide range of projects, including:\r\n\r\nReal-time ride-sharing and cab booking apps\r\n\r\nSocial media platforms with interactive user features\r\n\r\nHealth and fitness trackers with live activity monitoring\r\n\r\nVPN and chat applications with secure authentication and media sharing\r\n\r\nMy expertise spans across full-cycle development Рђћ from UI/UX design in Figma, to front-end implementation, to backend integration with technologies such as Firebase (Authentication, Firestore, Realtime Database, Storage), RESTful APIs, and advanced state management using Provider and Riverpod. I follow clean architecture principles (MVVM) to ensure code maintainability and scalability.\r\n\r\nI am currently focused on remote opportunities where I can contribute my technical experience, design sensibility, and problem-solving skills to a forward-thinking team. I am confident that my background and dedication to quality make me a strong candidate for this role.\r\n\r\nThank you for considering my application. I would welcome the opportunity to discuss how I can add value to your team. Please find my r├Еsum├Е and portfolio linked below.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nRashid Minhas\r\nhttps://github.com/RashidMinhas47\r\nhttps://rashidminhas.netlify.app/\r\nhttps://stackoverflow.com/users/20897980/rashid-minhas-sheikh\r\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/rashidminhassheikh/', '2025-06-04 09:05:58', '2025-06-04 09:05:58'),
