ion \r\nMain Delivery: \r\n \r\nUSB measurement module (1 pc.) - provides measurement control between hardware and software. \r\nVibration transducers (2 pcs.) - Conversion factor: 100 mV/g. Operating frequencies: 0.5-10,000 Hz. Mounting: threaded stud. \r\n \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9.webp\" alt=\"Accelerometer with magnetic base\" style=\"max-width: 50%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0;\"></a> \r\n \r\nLaser phase sensor (1 pc.) - Distance: up to 1.5 m. Contactless operation for safe operation. \r\n \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/11.webp\" alt=\"Laser tachometer MS2234\" style=\"max-width: 50%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0;\"></a> \r\n \r\nMagnetic mount for phase sensor (1 pc.) - Pull force: 60 kgf. Flexible mounting for accurate readings. \r\n \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/magnetiline-alus-insize-60-kgf-e0f05_reference-1.jpg\" alt=\"Professional magnetic stand\" style=\"max-width: 50%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0;\"></a> \r\n \r\nDigital scales up to 500 g (1 pc.) - Resolution: 0.01 g. Essential for precise weight measurement. \r\nProgram Balanset-1A - Easy-to-use design. Windows compatible. International versions. \r\n \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/wpforo/default_attachments/1747606106-Screenshot-2025-05-16-165601.png\" alt=\"Vibration analysis software\" style=\"max-width: 80%; height: auto; margin: 10px 0;\"></a> \r\n \r\nProtective case (1 pc.) - Durable construction. Protective padding for safe transport. \r\nOperating instructions - Comprehensive guide. Practical examples. \r\nConnection cables - High-quality shielded cables. \r\n \r\n \r\nBenefits of Balanset-1A \r\nTechnical Advantages: \r\n? High Accuracy - Modern algorithms of data analysis provide consistent accuracy. \r\n? Mobility - Light weight facilitates field operations without dismantling. \r\n? Wide Capabilities - Suitable for various rotors from small fans to massive shafts. \r\n? Ease of Use - Clear controls requires no lengthy education. \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714073479031.jpg\" alt=\"Professional vibration diagnostics\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 20px 0;\"></a> \r\nEconomic Effect: \r\n? Savings on maintenance through failure prevention - up to 70% of unplanned downtime. \r\n? Service Life Increase by 50-200% - vibration-free operation operates reliably. \r\n? Power Savings by 5-15% - reduced friction consume less power. \r\n? Fast Investment Return - from 3 to 12 months depending on application frequency. \r\n \r\nSupport \r\nAvailable to you: \r\nPersonnel Training - comprehensive sessions at your site. Certification program includes full procedures. \r\nExpert Assistance - remote help. Email support for immediate help. \r\nVerification and Calibration - periodic verification to maintain accuracy. \r\nDevice Leasing - ideal for short-term needs. Weekly rental options available. \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1714073478991.jpg\" alt=\"Professional vibration analysis\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 20px 0;\"></a> \r\n \r\nPrice Information \r\nActual Prices: \r\nBalanset-1A Portable Balancer & Vibration Analyzer: Рѓг1,751.00 \r\nBalanset-1A OEM Version: Рѓг1,561.00 \r\nAdditional Vibration Sensor: Рѓг90.00 \r\nOptical Sensor (Laser Tachometer): Рѓг124.00 \r\nMagnetic Stand 60 kgf: Рѓг46.00 \r\nReflective Tape: Рѓг10.00 \r\n<a href=\"https://vibromera.eu/shop/889/\"><img src=\"https://vibromera.eu/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/лЉл░л╗л║лЙл╝4-scaled-2.jpg\" alt=\"Professional balancing equipment\" style=\"max-width: 80%; height: auto; margin: 20px 0;\"></a> \r\nShipping Co