(3594, 'Saffet Erdogan', 'ceylanturks41@gmail.com', '88491992855', '-', '-', 'Request for Business Cooperation', 'Greetings, \r\n \r\nI am writing to present a brief biography about myself and to seek your business cooperation. \r\n \r\nI was born on 15 March 1968 in Turkey. I have lived a life defined by vision, resilience, and integrity. I am a devoted husband and a proud father of one son, and I embody the values of family, responsibility, and leadership in both my personal and professional journey. \r\n \r\nAs the Managing Director of a furniture manufacturing company and a towel and textile manufacturing company, I have built a reputation as a dynamic entrepreneur whose work combines creativity with discipline. My leadership style is marked by fairness, dedication, and a deep sense of responsibility toward my employees and business partners. I am admired for my ability to transform challenges into opportunities, guiding my businesses with wisdom and foresight. \r\n \r\nAs a Turkish Christian, I hold a strong belief in freedom of worship and advocate for respect, tolerance, and unity among people of different faiths. My spiritual values inspire me to live with compassion, humility, and a commitment to justice. I am known not only for my professional achievements but also for my moral strength and unwavering principles. \r\n \r\nMy personality reflects qualities that attract admiration: \r\n \r\n* Integrity and honesty in all dealings \r\n* Visionary leadership that inspires growth and innovation \r\n* Compassion and generosity, always mindful of the needs of others \r\n* Resilience and determination, never deterred by obstacles \r\n* Faith and humility, grounding success in values that transcend material wealth \r\n \r\nThrough my journey, I have become more than a successful businessmanРђћa role model of responsibility, a man of faith, and a beacon of perseverance. My life story continues to inspire those around me, proving that true greatness lies not only in achievements but in the character and values that sustain them. \r\n \r\nI am currently experiencing issues with the Turkish government, as the Government of Turkey is planning to confiscate my assets. Therefore, I wish to invest my funds, totaling 85,000,000 euros, with you. \r\n \r\nFor further information, I would appreciate it if you could write to me with a brief biography about yourself as well. Please write to me directly at this email address, as I have this email application on my phone and can read emails quickly and give a prompt reply: *<>esaffet81@gmail.com ]   (mailto: esaffet81@gmail.com)*. \r\n \r\nMy regards, \r\n \r\nMr. Saffet Erdogan', '2025-12-30 22:20:56', '2025-12-30 22:20:56'),
(3595, 'MichaelfoF', 'xrumer23Fup@gmail.com', '85573462455', '-', '-', 'evakuatorhelp', '<a href=https://evakuatorhelp.ru/>лил┤лхЛЂЛї</a>  лЮлх ЛѓЛђл░ЛѓЛїЛѓлх л▓Лђлхл╝ЛЈ лйл░ л┐лЙлИЛЂл║лИ л┤ЛђЛЃл│лИЛЁ л║лЙл╝л┐л░лйлИл╣, л║лЙл│л┤л░ л▓л░л╝ лйЛЃлХлхлй лйл░л┤лхлХлйЛІл╣ ЛЇл▓л░л║ЛЃл░ЛѓлЙЛђ л▓ лАлЪл▒. лЪЛђлЙЛЂЛѓлЙ л┐лЙлил▓лЙлйлИЛѓлх лйл░л╝ лИл╗лИ лЙЛЂЛѓл░л▓ЛїЛѓлх лил░ЛЈл▓л║ЛЃ лйл░ ЛЂл░л╣Лѓлх, лИ л╝ЛІ лЙл┐лхЛђл░ЛѓлИл▓лйлЙ л┐ЛђлИл┤лхл╝ л▓л░л╝ лйл░ л┐лЙл╝лЙЛЅЛї. люЛІ Лђл░л▒лЙЛѓл░лхл╝ 24 ЛЄл░ЛЂл░ л▓ ЛЂЛЃЛѓл║лИ, 7 л┤лйлхл╣ л▓ лйлхл┤лхл╗Лј, л▒лхли л▓ЛІЛЁлЙл┤лйЛІЛЁ лИ л┐Лђл░лил┤лйлИЛЄлйЛІЛЁ л┤лйлхл╣, ЛЄЛѓлЙл▒ЛІ л▓ЛІ л╝лЙл│л╗лИ л▒ЛІЛѓЛї ЛЃл▓лхЛђлхлйЛІ л▓ лйл░Лѕлхл╣ л┐лЙл┤л┤лхЛђлХл║лх л▓ л╗Лјл▒лЙлх л▓Лђлхл╝ЛЈ ЛЂЛЃЛѓлЙл║. лњЛІл▒лИЛђл░л╣Лѓлх л┐ЛђлЙЛёлхЛЂЛЂлИлЙлйл░л╗лЙл▓! люЛІ л│л░Лђл░лйЛѓлИЛђЛЃлхл╝ л▓ЛІЛЂлЙл║лЙлх л║л░ЛЄлхЛЂЛѓл▓лЙ лЙл▒ЛЂл╗ЛЃлХлИл▓л░лйлИЛЈ лИ л┤лЙЛЂЛѓЛЃл┐лйЛІлх ЛєлхлйЛІ. лЮл░Лѕл░ Лђлхл┐ЛЃЛѓл░ЛєлИЛЈ РђЊ ЛЇЛѓлЙ ЛђлхлиЛЃл╗ЛїЛѓл░Лѓ л╝лйлЙл│лЙл╗лхЛѓлйлхл╣ Лђл░л▒лЙЛѓЛІ лИ ЛЂлЙЛѓлхлй л┤лЙл▓лЙл╗ЛїлйЛІЛЁ л║л╗лИлхлйЛѓлЙл▓.', '2025-12-30 23:34:46', '2025-12-30 23:34:46'),
